{"tid":800756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不誠實取用電腦罪定義成疑　蕭源涉取DSE試題案明年續審】","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:09:59.000Z","uid":157103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"839d60bb6c9141ae6efdd28c71ef4248030df99d","tid":800756,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"補習天王蕭源（真名蕭志勇）因涉用手機收取文憑試保密資料及試題，被控不誠實取用電腦罪，案件今日（8月31日）於西九龍裁判法院續審。由於不誠實取用電腦罪定義近日受到質疑，控方申請將案件押後到明年1月4日再審。<br />\n<br />\n曾任考評局監考員，現職中文補習老師的蕭源妻子蔡怡（原名蔡盈盈），及兩名考評局前口試主考員亦被控以同樣罪名。 <br />\n<br />\n4名被告獲准繼續以2000元保釋，但毋須每星期再到警署報到，其他保釋條件不變。 <br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-31-2018/47840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-31-2018%2F47840&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=56ce7235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-31-2018/47840</a><br />\n<br />\n#補習 #蕭源 #不誠實取用電腦 #DSE #文憑試 #試題"},{"pid":"793a1d26a424b04d6c67bdedcb951de0a66c7e51","tid":800756,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"即係可以keep住教多一年？"},{"pid":"efac13f6c6719d31c90e19be1680ac50b3ecd687","tid":800756,"uid":179467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"有預感覺得doj最後要瘋狂申請更改控罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625cc1405ac64e687b82d2ba12a3aeba9bfd1343","tid":800756,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"見佢keep住出youtube片，好似好淡定咁"},{"pid":"ccec815e6899116c3d56b856fa3b26e0c9526e8a","tid":800756,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"緊係 打官司幫佢宣傳 <br />\n有料拎到試題 成班學生狗沖啦"},{"pid":"f4b5425a52c54f9f03e5c1be21c92d4162122ff1","tid":800756,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"咁今年即係未燒完？"}]}